onsidered as among the best renewable materials. When it comes to mature progress, bamboo grows quickly in tufts without the use of pesticide or human care. It takes just 3-5 years to regrow new bamboo generation that has been cut. Bamboo can exist in harsh climate condition and infertile soil and distribute mostly in Asia where ensures partly worldwide consumption demand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bamboo does grow in need of not much water. Although bamboo is willing to grow in wetland conditions, it can also be matured in places where other plants would require substantial watering to survive. Fresh water is a valuable resource on our planet, and bamboo is not a needy plant when considering water consumption.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/ckfinder/images/jhjhj.jpg\" style=\"height:768px; width:1024px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bamboo straws have recently become a trendy alternative resolution to plastic straws whose idea is the youths throughout the world. So what are bad impacts of plastic straws?</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Their main recipient is polypropylen that has no smell, no taste, no color and no poison. Neverthless, upon manufacture process, some additives, color makers, consistency makers&hellip;, if not under strict control of dose, can lead to harmful impact on human health.</li>\r\n	<li>Plastic straws discharge into lakes, rivers, streams or even seas, which contaminates sea environment, inflict enormous damage on fishing and tourism.</li>\r\n	<li>Using plastic straws along with hot drink gives cause to suffering from toxic chemicals such as TOCP, BPA&hellip;, congenital disorder in babies, early puberty, infertility or cancer&hellip;</li>\r\n	<li>They are not safe for young children, easily leave scratches adjacent to mouth if lack of parents&rsquo;surveillance.</li>\r\n	<li>Plastic straws exterminate a great number of sea animals. According to One Less Straw Organization, plastic straws kill more than 100.000 sea animals and millions of sea birds per year&hellip;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/ckfinder/images/Bamboo-Straw-Market-01-346x188.jpg\" style=\"height:188px; width:346px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Making bamboo straws process: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b0Qy4-bl7zA\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b0Qy4-bl7zA</a></p>','/e6/54/4e/5e91b9698e430.jpg',NULL,0,0,'2020-04-11 19:34:49',NULL,'Bamboo is considered as among the best renewable materials. When it comes to mature progress, bamboo grows quickly in tufts without the use of pesticide or human care.','bamboo, environment protection, bamboo straw','','',2,0,'en','how-bamboo-protect-environment',5,33,33,'2020-04-11 19:34:49','2020-04-11 19:34:49'),(242,'Benefits of water hyacinth cushion','','In this article, we would like to recommend one kind of cushion that is made of 100% natural material: Rattan cushion.','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\">Benefits of water hyacinth cushion</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A number of people are always seeking for outdoor or indoor cushion that is not only standing the test of time but also providing you with the taste of comfort. In modern global market, it is not difficult to find one that satisfies your requirement. There are abundant of suppliers, a wide range of goods source of different styles, designs, materials or item prices. Inadvertently, demand is big.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The problem is that which one is the most suitable for you? And what kind of cushion you are really pursuing? In this article, we would like to recommend one kind of cushion that is made of 100% natural material: Water hyacinth&nbsp;cushion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Durability</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/ckfinder/images/il_794xN_1964010298_qyut.jpg\" style=\"height:490px; width:794px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do not look down on that n